Reasoning: The paper deals with communication systems over fading channels, which is a topic covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Communications (cs.COMM) sub-categories. The algorithms presented for synchronization and channel estimation may fall under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. Finally, the use of massive MIMO suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category, as MIMO techniques are commonly used in wireless multimedia communication systems.
